    <td class="caption"><div class="article-title"><a href="http://link.aps.org/doi/10.1103/PhysRevA.87.010703"><img src="/shared/graphics/rapid.gif" alt ="Rapid icon"/>&nbsp; Feshbach spectroscopy of an ultracold mixture of <sup>85</sup>Rb and <sup>133</sup>Cs</a> </div><div class="article-teaser" style ="font-style:italic;"></div><div class="article-teaser">We report the observation of interspecies Feshbach resonances in an optically trapped mixture of <sup>85</sup>Rb and <sup>133</sup>Cs. We measure nine resonances in the lowest spin channel for a magnetic field range from 0 to 700 G and show that they are in good agreement with coupled-channel calculations. The interspeci...<br/>[Phys. Rev. A 87, 010703 (2013)] Published Fri Jan 11, 2013
</div><p class="article-read-more"><a href="http://link.aps.org/doi/10.1103/PhysRevA.87.010703">Read Rapid</a> | <a onClick="$('#rapids-link').trigger('click')" href="#tabcontent-rapid-communications">More Rapid Communications</a></div></td> </tr> </tbody> </table><br/>                    
